#. ~ Description for scenario 'Cruise of the Dead' for a male character.
#: .\oa_scenarios.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You finally saved up enough money to take that cruise around New England "
"that you always dreamed about; only to find yourself on a ship overrun with "
"the undead! Fight your way out and swim to safety!"
msgstr "你终于攒够了钱，去参加梦寐以求的新英格兰环游之旅；却发现整艘船已被亡灵占领！杀出一条血路，游向安全地带吧！"

